Open Source

At the NLnet Labs foundation, we develop software for the benefit of the Internet, enhancing its stability and security.

Open Standards

NLnet Labs contributes to developing open standards that strengthen the Internet’s architecture.

Research

Using our expertise, NLnet Labs participates in research projects and Internet measurements.

Education

NLnet Labs mentors student projects, hosts training courses and offers advice to organisations about Internet infrastructure.
